Rebel in the Rye is a 2017 American biographical drama film directed and written by Danny Strong .
It is based on the book J. D. Salinger : A Life by Kenneth Slawenski , about the life of young writer J. D. Salinger during World War II .
The film stars Nicholas Hoult , Zoey Deutch , Kevin Spacey , Sarah Paulson , Brian d'Arcy James , Victor Garber , Hope Davis , and Lucy Boynton .
Principal photography on the film began on April 26 , 2016 in New York City .
It premiered at the 2017 Sundance Film Festival on January 24 , 2017 .